_fastData.content: Hack for typetemplate default parameter bug. Input propagated to arrayinuser.
Base resource for reading from array/arraycontainer structures (depending on port types allowed by core node).

Special case for Array type inputs, they don't carry a name of meaningful id. 
So we just give a string to that id. Array type input use case always have a single value
input, compared to ArrayContainer type input which carry a more meaningful id.

Base resource for writing to array/arraycontainer structures (depending on port types allowed by core node).
Scope ports included on top of readbase resource..
